亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是來自維多利亞的記者吧？", "name": "溫和的謝拉格人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近謝拉格不太安穩，連本地人都更願意躲在家裡，你得小心了。", "name": "溫和的謝拉格人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但越到這種時候，就越不能夠恐懼，否則我就不配拿起相機。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還是感謝您的提醒。不過我想瞭解的是，如今您對恩希歐迪斯最真實的看法是？", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……抱歉，維多利亞的記者，我覺得他欺騙了謝拉格人，但維多利亞確實值得懷疑。", "name": "溫和的謝拉格人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多年來，謝拉格改變有多大我也看在眼裡，要是說恩希歐迪斯大人沒有苦衷顯然也不屬實。", "name": "溫和的謝拉格人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是蔓珠院的大長老現在能出來說兩句話就好了——", "name": "溫和的謝拉格人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_278_1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_throwstone"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windowbreak"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_278_1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-200,0", "focus": "all", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突如其來的石塊幾乎劃過記者的鼻尖，它徑直撞破後方的店鋪櫥窗。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "shake", "power": 2.0, "times": 70.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞滾出謝拉格！", "name": "憤怒的謝拉格人"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯、蔓珠院、我們，都和你沒有半點關係！", "name": "憤怒的謝拉格人"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還敢再拍？給我*謝拉格俚語*滾！", "name": "憤怒的謝拉格人"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有什麼比這一刻更令她五味雜陳。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到平凡生活中的謝拉格人，漸漸變得多疑、煩躁。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她更看到了曾經推心置腹的攝製團隊成員們，竟潛入她的房間，對著她的稿紙和相機反覆檢視……"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "posfrom": "-70,0", "posto": "150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當男人再次掏出一塊石頭，記者朝受訪者鞠躬告別，跑離了現場……"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎只有逃跑這一種選擇……然而，她又能逃到哪裡？"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐，你是維多利亞人嗎？", "name": "謝拉格兒童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……小朋友，你好。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#4$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你，不討厭維多利亞嗎？", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我不討厭。", "name": "謝拉格兒童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "髒兮兮的小手遞過來一塊硬掉的維多利亞麵包。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是爸爸和我說，要把這些全部丟掉，我們家絕不能要維多利亞人施捨的東西。", "name": "謝拉格兒童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但耶拉岡德教導我們，謝拉格人要愛自己的鄰人，還要知恩圖報。", "name": "謝拉格兒童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我想把它還給你。", "name": "謝拉格兒童"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2002_1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2002_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "望著匆匆離去的孩子的背影，記者彷彿被手中的乾麵包噎住了咽喉，她眼瞼微顫，牙關緊鎖……"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_stickimp"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "67_G4_kjeragstreet", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 100.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.1, "duration": 5.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.2, "fillto": 1.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把她帶上車，別被人發現。", "name": "模糊的聲音"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是她昏迷前，能記得的最後的聲音。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "45_g11_karlanheadquarters", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉又來上門叨擾了，恩希歐迪斯先生。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許在這焦頭爛額的緊要關頭，你更想見其他人……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這話說得太見外了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格曾承蒙你的關照，我正想尋找機會當面致謝。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡……這次來謝拉格故地重遊，也是感慨萬千啊。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次我都想帶來一些好消息，再把這身老骨頭丟到雪山裡清淨一下。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但世事無常，總得學會即興，不是嗎？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我想，子爵閣下應該也不是為了開斯特公爵，而傳達壞消息給我的。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，那個老太婆的事，我再也不想插手了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然從我上次來到謝拉格的狀況看……應該是她更不願意讓我插手。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，子爵閣下……", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，說正事說正事，我知道你很忙。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是來向你告別的，恩希歐迪斯先生。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是近期關於維多利亞的輿論為您帶來了麻煩，我可以——", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不……不只是這樣……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我原本抱著一丁點不切實際的期待，想著老太婆也到了“其言也善”的年紀。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那總該真表示點善心吧？但你看，最後還是鬧成了現在這樣。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然會顯得我老糊塗了，但我忍不住想當面問你一句……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的沒有別的辦法了嗎？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#12$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，你知道她的企圖，並非幾片礦場而已。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從對恩希亞動手開始，這便已經是我無法接受的談判。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#9$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你打算怎麼對付她呢？難道真的準備和她刀兵相見？", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#15$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下比我清楚，如果不把“刀兵相見”作為一種底線，或許謝拉格已經是她的囊中之物了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "我當然……"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#16$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "唉，該說什麼比較好呢。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老太婆的脾氣嘛，你和她鬧到這個份上，她也絕不會善罷甘休。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#3$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恩希歐迪斯大人，我也是發自內心地為您擔憂，接下來該怎麼辦啊。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#11$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了“順勢而為”，又能怎麼辦呢？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，閣下和開斯特公爵也算相識已久了吧？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "我？"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "哈洛德", "content": "不熟不熟不熟。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前幾年倒會聊聊家常，她總和我提那些小開斯特們，牙癢癢地說就沒一個成器的。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越沒有成器的，她做起事也就越著急，誰能想到她年輕時那叫一個深不可測……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十多年前，我也和公爵閣下有一面之緣，她的高貴姿態猶在眼前。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，和我就沒必要這麼講了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都懂的，她那股高高在上的貴族作風根本不可能改。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背地裡算計再多，明面上也得搞出一副高傲體面的樣子。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#14$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好了，你的下屬還有更要緊的事麻煩你，我也該離開了。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……和閣下交流，受益匪淺。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#11$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望，能在未來有更恰當的時機邀請閣下造訪謝拉格。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，那就再好不過了！", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#4$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，對了……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（壓低聲音）你見到公爵閣下的時候，千萬別告訴她，我背地裡叫她老太婆哦。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然，子爵閣下。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_172_svrash_1#10$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，當然……", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是真的盼望，還有機會能再次拜訪謝拉格。", "name": "哈洛德"}, "figure_art": "avg_4114_harold_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g5_guestroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "24_g5_guestroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，沒有人發現。", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不為難，夫人的要求我一定……", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在就把她帶過來。", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，醒醒！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.4, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 1.0, "fillto": 0.4, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.4, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.4, "fillto": 0.0, "grad": "true", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "24_g5_guestroom", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我，這是，記得在——", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#12$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睡這麼久還沒睡飽啊？趕快起來，我們夫人有話問你。", "name": "布朗陶家護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰，找我……", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，你下手什麼時候才能分清楚輕重？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對、對不起。", "name": "布朗陶家護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大夫人。", "name": "布朗陶家護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_284_1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，現在清醒點了嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別亂動，除非你嫌手上的繩子勒得不夠痛。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，菈塔托絲！", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……菈塔托絲大人，我以為你——", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到我沒有一處是燒焦的，很驚訝吧？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有機會的話告訴你的同事，和布朗陶家打交道時，最好檢查一下房間裡的機關。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的……同事？", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#11$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實交代吧，小間諜，你鬼鬼祟祟那麼多天，究竟想拍到些什麼？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……不，您誤會了！我怎麼會是間諜呢？！", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#6$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個被抓住的間諜都是這麼跟我說的。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旁的護衛從記者的背包拿出一些東西甩到了地上——是她這麼多天來拍攝、沖洗出來的照片。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍拍風土人情，甚至巡邏的家丁，倒也懶得管你。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你毫無顧忌，不但在蔓珠院裡拍了一路，甚至還跑進幾座山裡到處按快門。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別以為我什麼都不知道。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲大人，不管你是否相信，我真的只是一名普通記者。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#2$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我真的是間諜，那我為什麼要隨身攜帶這些物證在街上閒逛？", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況現在局勢如此混亂，我完全可以把這些全部交給電視台的同事保管。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你需要解釋的了，記者。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實是你攜帶著大量的可疑資料，行蹤詭異，我怎麼知道你是不是想逃跑？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#7$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我在保護這些資料！", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開斯特公爵想控制輿情，新聞辦公室便派人進駐攝製團隊，他們修改、刪除、剪輯我拍攝的內容，搜查我的房間。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不逃跑，你看到的絕大多數資料都會被他們沒收，甚至被斷章取義。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們做的這一切，最終都是為了洗白維多利亞想要強行介入謝拉格內政的行為！", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#7$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菈塔托絲大人，如果你覺得這些資料還有利於謝拉格，我可以全部交給你。", "name": "維多利亞記者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維多利亞記者", "content": "只要你能把這些內容發布出去，讓更多人知道，謝拉格正在發生什麼……"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2006_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維多利亞記者", "content": "它不需要維多利亞人的“協助”，而是需要真正的幫助！"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#2$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難辦了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#5$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種時候，恩希歐迪斯還能接電話嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#9$1"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有更要緊的事需要處理，所以只派了我來支援。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假死之後，我抓的這幾個間諜也都交給他了，按照約定他早就得派人來支援我了。", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "結果只派了一個人，但來的卻是黑騎士。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "菈塔托絲", "content": "我到底該說他是大方還是小氣呢……"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對付開斯特公爵，他現在有什麼主意？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#4$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在收集敵人的資訊，派我來幫你審問也有這個原因。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在最關鍵的是，這位記者到底有沒有拍到“山裡的東西”。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，這位朋友……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以先幫你鬆綁，也請你保證……", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#10$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_253_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我接下來的提問有問必答，好嗎？", "name": "菈塔托絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_253_1#11$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}